1 Day Ago But before his situation got worse, Ikpeazu made attempts to be flown abroad but the restriction on international flights ban in many countries around the world and his positive status of the virus put paid to that move. Though he is believed to be in a stable condition at the moment, he is said to still be a long way from full recovery.